commit.title: Fixing #12223 which was fixing #12152 (locating atomic tactics).
commit.message:
Fixing #12223 which was fixing #12152 (locating atomic tactics).

The update of a loc was done in the wrong direction: overriding a more
precise one rather than setting when there was none.

In some situations, this was going to a tclOR which was even setting
the loc to a disjoint part of the code.
